dct_title_s: Plan of the foreign concessions Tientsin
dct_description_sm: Drawn and Engraved for the Directory & Chronicle ; John Bartholomew & Co., Edinr.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows roads (including projected), various locations (stations, temples), railways, hospitals, vegetation, waterways.
Note on map: "This part is reserved for further extension of the Japanese Concession, but is now under the jurisdiction of the Chinese authorities."
Map removed from "Directory & Chronicle," likely 1903 edition.
